    "2026-05-15: RU log smoke test: P3_2=Деревня Криар -> i2_mount_cryer; P3_4=Воющие пещеры -> i2_glacial_tarn; P3_3 now maps to interlude_glacial_tarn; P3_5 stays mapped to Kriar Peaks.",
    "2026-05-15: fixed Interlude 3 RU mapping: P3_2=Деревня Криар(+40 духа), P3_4=Воющие пещеры(Йети/пассивки), P3_5=Пики Криар(опциональный уник); P3_3=Ледниковое озеро -> interlude_glacial_tarn.",
    "2026-05-15: current RU scene names patched: Вольфенхолд -> i_final_wolvenholt; Машинариум Джиквани -> a3_jiquani_machinarium.",
    "2026-05-16: fixed Act 1 internal area mapping: G1_11/C_G1_11 -> Hunting Grounds, G1_12/C_G1_12 -> Freythorn, G1_13_1 -> Ogham Farmlands; also synced G1_5/G1_6 and G1_8/G1_9 with conservative mapping.",
    "2026-05-17: added guide cards for Mud Burrow, Lightless Passage, Temple of Chaos, Trial of the Ancestors, Plunder's Point, and Interlude side zones; Kedge Bay/Kid's Bay wording intentionally unchanged.",
    "2026-05-24: added P1_1/C_P1_1 -> Scorched Farmlands and fixed Interlude 1/2 route chain names.",
    "2026-05-24: added P3_Town/C_P3_Town -> The Glade and P3_1/C_P3_1 -> Ashen Forest for the Kriar branch route.",
    "2026-05-24: added P2_Town/C_P2_Town -> Khari Bazaar and P1_Town/C_P1_Town -> The Refuge; route now goes Heart of the Tribe -> Khari Bazaar and Cuachic Vault -> Refuge.",
    "2026-05-24: added hub guide mappings for G1/G2/G3 towns and removed Dreadnought Vanguard from the active 0.5 route."
  ],
